nodes.title: INSTRUCTIONS
widgets_values:
INSTRUCTIONS : 
Your task is to generate 20 unique and highly varied image generation prompts based EXCLUSIVELY on the provided subject in the image. These prompts must be optimized for models like FLUX.1 Kontext to ensure strong subject consistency and diverse scenarios. Crucially, strictly infer the subject type (Character or Product) AND GENDER (for Characters) ONCE from the input string and apply that consistently to ALL 20 generated prompts. Each prompt must begin with the appropriate consistency prefix.

Input:

A single, concise string representing the subject for all 20 prompts. This string MUST NOT include clothing descriptions if the subject is a character (e.g., "a determined medieval knight", "a young woman"). It must implicitly or explicitly define the character (e.g., "a man with a goatee", "a young woman", "a female adventurer") or product (e.g., "a sleek, futuristic drone", "a vintage camera", "a pink shampoo bottle"). Your internal logic MUST be able to infer Male, Female, or N/A (Product) from this string.

Output:

Deliver ONLY a single block of 20 distinct image generation prompts. Each prompt on a new line, immediately followed by the next prompt on the subsequent line. ABSOLUTELY NO empty lines between prompts, NO introductory text whatsoever, NO concluding text, and NO other formatting, explanations, or commentary.

Prompt Construction Logic
For each of the 20 prompts, combine elements from the following categories. Ensure a wide variety across the entire set to maximize visual diversity, maintaining the single inferred Subject Type and Gender for all 20 prompts.

Subject Integration & Consistency Prefix (with Gender Adaptation for Characters):

If Subject Type is Character (Male): Start the prompt with: "Keep exact same character, [provided subject string], a photo of him..."

If Subject Type is Character (Female): Start the prompt with: "Keep exact same character, [provided subject string], a photo of her..."

If Subject Type is Product: Start the prompt with: "Keep exact same product, [provided subject string], a photo of it..."

Character-Specific Consistency: Add "maintaining original facial features and body structure", "with consistent appearance", or "true to his/her likeness" (adapting pronoun based on inferred gender) where natural.

Product-Specific Constraint: Ensure no human or animal attributes/actions (e.g., no "smiling", "running", "wearing"). Focus on its form, material, lighting, and placement.

Context/Placement (Choose one from varied options):

Urban (e.g., bustling city square, modern rooftop, neon-lit alley)

Natural (e.g., dense forest, mountain trail, beach, lakeside)

Fantasy/Sci-Fi (e.g., ancient ruin, spaceship bridge, alien planet)

Specific setting (e.g., cozy cafe, minimalist apartment, workbench, gallery display)

Character-only contexts: running dynamically, interacting with a pet, preparing a meal.

Product-only contexts: placed on countertop, resting on desk, mounted on wall.

Action/Expression/State (Choose one; CRUCIAL FOR DIVERSITY; strict type adherence & Gender Adaptation):

For Character Subjects ONLY:

Expressions: with a confident smirk, lost in thought, gentle smile, with a look of surprise, deep in focused concentration, with a serious contemplation.

Actions/Poses: reading intently, sketching passionately, gesturing expressively, leaping gracefully, dancing joyfully, with a relaxed posture, interacting with a pet, preparing a meal, immersed in a complex project, observing a grand painting.

Varying Attire (Choose one): wearing a stylish leather jacket / an elegant evening gown / casual summer clothes / a futuristic uniform / worn medieval armor / a cozy knit sweater / athletic sportswear / a sharp business suit.

Prioritize diversity of facial expressions, body poses, AND clothing styles.

For Product Subjects ONLY:

States: gleaming under spotlights, partially hidden in tall grass, weathered by time, freshly painted, emitting a soft glow, in mid-air, casting a long shadow, reflecting the environment, functioning precisely, standing majestically, glowing faintly, covered in frost, illuminating the surroundings, displaying intricate patterns, resting quietly.

Prioritize diversity of states and visual attributes, NOT human-like actions/expressions.

Shot Type/Angle (Choose one; ENSURE MAXIMUM DIVERSITY IN PERSPECTIVE):

Low angle: a dynamic low-angle shot (camera looking up from below), a worm's-eye view (camera on the ground, looking up).

Eye-level/Standard: an eye-level cinematic shot (camera at the subject's eye level), a 3/4 view (classic, balanced perspective), a front view (straight on), a back view (from behind), a side view (directly from left/right).

High angle: a high-angle shot (camera above, looking down), a bird's-eye view (camera directly above).

Framing: a full body shot (Character only), an extreme close-up (tightly framed on detail), a tight close-up (framed on main body/face), a sweeping wide shot (showing scale), a dramatic profile shot, a macro shot (Product only).

Narrative: an intimate over-the-shoulder shot (looking at subject from behind another element), a point of view (POV) shot (from subject's/another's perspective).

Prioritize unique angles/framings for each prompt.

Lighting/Atmosphere/Style (Add 1-2 highly descriptive terms for richness):

General: high fidelity, photorealistic, sharp focus, intricate details.

Lighting: golden hour, soft studio illumination, dramatic volumetric, stark chiaroscuro, industrial.

Atmosphere: atmospheric haze, dreamy bokeh, moody blues, ethereal dawn light.

Style: gritty street photography, vibrant neon glow, cinematic film look, vibrant pop art, sleek product photography, rustic natural light.

Final Prompt Formulation
Combine the selected elements into a single, cohesive prompt string. Ensure grammatical correctness and natural flow. The goal is 20 distinct, high-quality, type-appropriate prompts.

All output MUST strictly follow these rules:

Deliver ONLY a single block of 20 distinct image generation prompts.

Each prompt on a new line, immediately followed by the next prompt on the subsequent line.

ABSOLUTELY NO empty lines between prompts.

NO introductory text, NO concluding text, NO additional formatting, NO explanations, and NO commentary.

Example of expected output format (based on inferred gender/type):
Keep exact same character, a curious young woman, a photo of her with a confident smirk, wearing a stylish leather jacket, in a cozy cafe corner, Shot Type: eye-level cinematic shot, warm cozy glow, high fidelity, maintaining original facial features and body structure.
Keep exact same product, a sleek, futuristic drone, a photo of it in mid-air above a rugged mountain trail, Shot Type: worm's-eye view, dramatic volumetric lighting, reflecting the environment, no human elements.
Keep exact same character, a medieval knight, a photo of him with a serious contemplation, wearing worn medieval armor, inside a medieval castle hall, Shot Type: high-angle shot, moody blues, intricate details, true to his likeness.
(... and so on, for a total of 20 lines, with no breaks or extra text.)
